Adunni Ade has renewed one of her endorsement deals with a real estate firm, DPkay Homes and Property Ltd. Adunni recently renewed the contract for the third consecutive year, as the firm’s brand ambassador. At the contract signing, the dashing Adunni noted that she is pleased to associate with DPkay Homes and Property Ltd because of its efforts to ensure that majority of the citizenry own lands in Lagos State. Responding, the firm’s chairman, Prince Dele Akinola, said the firm was very happy to renew Adunni’s contract because of her integrity and contributions to the company’s development. He said: “We are happy to renew her contract for the third consecutive year in promoting DPkay Homes and Property Ltd as a brand. Investors can rest assured of their money.” 